<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" /><!--viewport网页缩放-->
	<meta charset="utf-8" /><!-- UTF-8编码 -->
	<meta name="keywords" content="珠宝租赁" /><!-- 关键词 -->
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" /><!-- 禁用自动识别电话号码 -->
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" /><!-- 强制全屏 -->
	<meta name="msapplication-tap-highlight" content="no" /><!-- 禁用点击高光效果 -->
    <title>预定订单确认</title>
     <link rel="stylesheet" media="screen and (max-width:330px)" href="../../../baseConfig/base320.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" media="screen and (min-width:331px) and (max-width:380px)" href="../../../baseConfig/base360.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" media="screen and (min-width:381px)" href="../../../baseConfig/base414.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet/less" href="reservedOrderConfirm.less" />
    <script src="../../../lib/js/less-1.3.3.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="../../../lib/js/zepto.min.js" type="text/javascript" ></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="topText" >
		预定货品到货后我们会根据您选定的时间联系您取货/送货上门，请留意预定时间，谢谢！
	</div>
<div class="orderConfirm_cont">
	<div class="order_type">
		购买
	</div>
	<div class="order_main">
		<div class="img">
			<img src="images/order.png"/>
		</div>
		<div class="order_right">
			<h2>美憾凡尘PT50铂金阶梯经典钻石订婚戒指</h2>
			<p>这一青春永恒的象征守护无限的爱</p>
			<p>奢华款，2克拉</p>
			<h3>会员价<span>￥52000</span><i>X 1</i></h3>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="total">
		<p><span>共一件商品</span>合计:<i>￥52000</i></p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="message">
	<h2>买家留言</h2>
	<textarea placeholder="给商家留言（100字以内）"></textarea>
	<p>根据预定规则，您需要先支付</p>
</div>
<div class="discount">
	<div class="coupon">
		<p>优惠券：满10000减100</p>
		<i class="iconfont">&#xe626;</i>
	</div>
	<div class="loan">
		<p>银行贷款申请</p>
		<i class="iconfont">&#xe626;</i>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="totalNum">
	<p>商品金额<span>￥52000</span></p>
	<p>定金比例<span>20%</span></p>
	<h3>需支付定金<span>￥3200</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="submit">
	<span id="" class="confirmPay">
		确认付款
	</span>
	<span id="" class="negotiation">
		好友代付（请一位好友替您支付）
	</span>
</div>
</body>
    <script src="reservedOrderConfirm.js" type="text/javascript" ></script>
</html>